# Review and Triage

Two-phase workflow: (1) multi-specialist code review of uncommitted changes, (2) triage findings into prioritized td issues under an epic.

## Arguments

```
/pre-landing-check [epic-id-or-name] [optional file/area focus]
```

- **epic-id-or-name** (optional): td epic ID (e.g., `td-a0ba4f`) or name to search for. If omitted, ask the user.
- **file/area focus** (optional): specific file path or area to focus the review on.

